com.opensymphony.xwork2.config.providers

Class XmlDocConfigurationProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opensymphony.xwork2.config.providers.XmlDocConfigurationProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationProvider, ContainerProvider, PackageProvider
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    XmlConfigurationProvider

    public abstract class XmlDocConfigurationProvider
extends Object
implements ConfigurationProvider
    This is a base XWork2 ConfigurationProvider for loading configuration from a parsed XML document. By extending this class, configuration can be loaded from any source that an XML document can be parsed from. Note that this class does not validate the document against any provided DTDs. For loading configuration from an XML file with DTD validation, please see StrutsXmlConfigurationProvider.
    Since:
    6.2.0
